ya.php|archive-date=9 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|commander1= {{flagicon|Libya}} [[Fayez al-Sarraj]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://africa.tvcnews.tv/2016/09/02/head-libyas-unity-government-visits-sirte/|title=Head of Libya's Unity Government visits Sirte|first=Tvc|last=News|date=2 September 2016|accessdate=3 October 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160924084705/http://africa.tvcnews.tv/2016/09/02/head-libyas-unity-government-visits-sirte/|archive-date=24 September 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref><br /><small>(Head of Unity Government)</small><br />{{flagicon|Libya}} Colonel [[Al-Mahdi Al-Barghathi]]<ref>Norbrook, Nicholas. [http://www.theafricareport.com/North-Africa/libyan-army-gains-ground-against-is-in-sirte.html Libyan army gains ground against IS in Sirte] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628034540/http://www.theafricareport.com/North-Africa/libyan-army-gains-ground-against-is-in-sirte.html |date=2016-06-28}}. ''[[The Africa Report]]''. Published 22 June 2016. Retrieved 30 June 2016.</ref><br /><small>(GNA Minister of Defense)</small><br />{{flagicon|Libya}} [[Rida Issa]]<ref name=\"navy\"/><br /><small>(GNA navy commander)</small><br />{{flagicon|Libya}} [[Ibrahim Baitulmal]]<br /><small>(Head of Misrata military council)</small><ref name=Reuters1>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-libya-security-idUSKCN1162RO|title=Libyan forces prepare for last push against Islamic State in Sirte|date=31 August 2016|publisher=|accessdate=3 October 2016|via=Reuters|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190624184302/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-libya-security-idUSKCN1162RO|archive-date=24 June 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><br />{{flagicon|Libya}} [[Ismail Shukri]]<br /><small>(Head of military intelligence in Misrata)</small><ref name=Reuters1/><br />{{flagicon|Libya}} Abdul Adeem al-Maadani{{KIA}}<ref name=\"al-Maadani\" /><br /><small>(Misrata Brigades senior commander)</small><br />{{flagicon|Libya}} Mohammed Issa<r